fields.name: Sun
fields.description: Archetype of self. Whatever is primary, central. That which elucidates. Truth.

fields.name: Moon
fields.description: Archetype of nurturer. Home and resources. Protection. The physical body. Scopes of all kinds, such as scope of perspective; worldview. Darkness. That which empathizes and reflects.

fields.name: Mercury
fields.description: Archetype of messenger. Communications and networks. Interpretation. Atomization, articulation, and expression. Skills, trade and fine motor tasks.

fields.name: Venus
fields.description: Archetype of lover. Beauty and balance. Feminine energy. Taste, aesthetics and choice. Relationships and connection of all kinds.

fields.name: Mars
fields.description: Archetype of warrior. Assertion and intervention. Masculine energy. Battles, struggles and disconnection of all kinds.

fields.name: Jupiter
fields.description: Archetype of growth. Gregarity and generosity. In the context of collective society, that which facilitates growth and connection. Joy, joviality. Good will. Public speaker. Motivational speaker. Saint. Entertainer.

fields.name: Saturn
fields.description: Archetype of restriction. Boundaries, structures, restriction and support of all kinds. In the context of collective society, that which judges, challenges and limits. Hard and dry. Limitation, struggle, and resilience. Mastery through effort. Monk. Stoic. Teacher. Wisdom

fields.name: Uranus
fields.description: Archetype of change. Rebellion, freedom and uniqueness. High energy that disrupts the status-quo. Insight, invention and ingenuity. The rebel.

fields.name: Neptune
fields.description: Archetype of transcendance. Meditation, spirit and illusion alike. The intangible. Higher truth and belief. The mystic.

fields.name: Pluto
fields.description: Archetype of power. The cycle of death and rebirth. Transformative energy. Explosion, obsession, and the deepest depths. Intensifies what it touches. Danger but potential.

fields.name: Chiron
fields.description: Archetype of healer. Weakness, unhealable wounds and unresolved trauma or conflict. Deep emotional understanding. Existential angst and the abyss. Humility and overcoming. The shaman.
